OL,4,G2100FSpain with Michael Portillo
OL,5,     GMichael visits Valencia, where he
OL,6,     Gtakes a lesson in bellringing,
OL,7,     Gtastes esmorzar, explores a
OL,8,     Gfavourite Spanish park, cooks
OL,9,     Gauthentic paella, and unveils the
OL,10,     Gcity's silk heritage.
OL,11,G2200FCrete: Jewel of the Med
OL,12,     GJoanna Lumley narrates this
OL,13,     Gexploration of the largest of the
OL,14,     GGreek Islands, taking in turtle
OL,15,     Gnesting sites, the ancient Palace
OL,16,     Gof Knossos, cuisine, culture,
OL,17,     Gwindmills and musical traditions.
