OL,4,G2300FNazi Megastructures
OL,5,     GIn a bid to dominate the Pacific,
OL,6,     GJapan builds the Yamato: the
OL,7,     Gbiggest battleship in the world,
OL,8,     Gwith the most powerful guns and
OL,9,     Gthe thickest armour ever mounted
OL,10,     Gon a warship.
OL,11,G0000FWentworth Prison
OL,12,     GWith the prison in lockdown,
OL,13,     Gtensions reach crisis point.
OL,14,G0100FThe Yorkshire Vet
OL,15,     GPampered papillon Belle is out of
OL,16,     Gsorts, while Snakee the corn
OL,17,     Gsnake has an unusual lump and a
OL,18,     Ghostile look in his eye.
